MVC Model -> Model View Controller -> Main Goal is to break the application into Smaller and specific sections
Model-> Layer connected to Database and responsible for application data logic and storing and retrieving data from Database
View-> Represent the UI to which the User interact with the application
Controller-> Controls the application logic neccassary for communications between the view and Model
